					<description><![CDATA[Certainly, there is a lot less &quot;work&quot; required to produce a low content or no content book compared with a technical work or a fiction story but I definitely put a lot of work into the ones I produce, simply because I want my books to be different from all the other ones available. Having said that, I really enjoy creating adult coloring, kids puzzle and journals / workbooks. It&#039;s not like work at all, when you are enjoying yourself. And so speaks someone who has wanted to be an author since she was 8 years old, which was a VERY long time ago. Now I have a shelf full of books with my name on the cover.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Certainly, there is a lot less &#8220;work&#8221; required to produce a low content or no content book compared with a technical work or a fiction story but I definitely put a lot of work into the ones I produce, simply because I want my books to be different from all the other ones available. Having said that, I really enjoy creating adult coloring, kids puzzle and journals / workbooks. It&#8217;s not like work at all, when you are enjoying yourself. And so speaks someone who has wanted to be an author since she was 8 years old, which was a VERY long time ago. Now I have a shelf full of books with my name on the cover.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
