					<description><![CDATA[In reply to &lt;a href=&quot;https://wordcounter.net/blog/2016/04/28/101247_no-content-books.html#comments/4647&quot;&gt;Toby&lt;/a&gt;.

This market has been saturated. Anyone trying to get int adult coloring books at this time will fail because everyone has already heard and tried to make money with them. In order to make money with no or low content books, you need to stay ahead of the curve and find a new niche before the hoards descend upon it. It&#039;s not easy, but that&#039;s where the money is. Following everyone else will leave you penniless.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In reply to <a href="https://wordcounter.net/blog/2016/04/28/101247_no-content-books.html#comments/4647">Toby</a>.</p>
<p>This market has been saturated. Anyone trying to get int adult coloring books at this time will fail because everyone has already heard and tried to make money with them. In order to make money with no or low content books, you need to stay ahead of the curve and find a new niche before the hoards descend upon it. It&#8217;s not easy, but that&#8217;s where the money is. Following everyone else will leave you penniless.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
