			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>How can anyone &#8220;write&#8221; a book if there is no content? That makes no sense at all. It&#8217;s not really a book if there isn&#8217;t any writing since words are what define a book. Without any words, it&#8217;s just blank pages.</p>
